Nice gesture.. but stupid

Most people with PSP already have a lot of games, so this will never ever be seeded properly, since everyone will skip all the games they have.

Splitting into A-D, E-J etc, 25gb each is a much better idea.

My advice.. redo it before wasting any more bandwidth.
